verses.text: The sons of Levi ; Gershon , Kohath , and Merari.\f + \fr 6.1 \ft Gershon: or, Gershom\f*
And the sons of Kohath ; Amram , Izhar , and Hebron , and Uzziel.
And the children of Amram ; Aaron , and Moses , and Miriam. The sons also of Aaron ; Nadab , and Abihu , Eleazar , and Ithamar. \p
¶ Eleazar begat Phinehas , Phinehas begat Abishua ,
And Abishua begat Bukki , and Bukki begat Uzzi ,
And Uzzi begat Zerahiah , and Zerahiah begat Meraioth ,
Meraioth begat Amariah , and Amariah begat Ahitub ,
And Ahitub begat Zadok , and Zadok begat Ahimaaz ,
And Ahimaaz begat Azariah , and Azariah begat Johanan ,
And Johanan begat Azariah , (he \add it is\add* that executed the priest’s office in the temple that Solomon built in Jerusalem :)\f + \fr 6.10 \ft in the temple: Heb. in the house\f*
And Azariah begat Amariah , and Amariah begat Ahitub ,
And Ahitub begat Zadok , and Zadok begat Shallum ,\f + \fr 6.12 \ft Shallum: or, Meshullam\f*
And Shallum begat Hilkiah , and Hilkiah begat Azariah ,
And Azariah begat Seraiah , and Seraiah begat Jehozadak ,
And Jehozadak went \add into captivity\add*, when the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* carried away Judah and Jerusalem by the hand of Nebuchadnezzar. \p
¶ The sons of Levi ; Gershom , Kohath , and Merari.\f + \fr 6.16 \ft Gershom: or, Gershon\f*
And these \add be\add* the names of the sons of Gershom ; Libni , and Shimei.
And the sons of Kohath \add were\add*, Amram , and Izhar , and Hebron , and Uzziel.
The sons of Merari ; Mahli , and Mushi. And these \add are\add* the families of the Levites according to their fathers.
Of Gershom ; Libni his son , Jahath his son , Zimmah his son ,
Joah his son , Iddo his son , Zerah his son , Jeaterai his son.\f + \fr 6.21 \ft Joah: or, Ethan\f*\f + \fr 6.21 \ft Iddo: or, Adaiah\f*\f + \fr 6.21 \ft Jeaterai: also called, Ethni\f*
The sons of Kohath ; Amminadab his son , Korah his son , Assir his son ,\f + \fr 6.22 \ft Amminadab: or, Izhar\f*
Elkanah his son , and Ebiasaph his son , and Assir his son ,
Tahath his son , Uriel his son , Uzziah his son , and Shaul his son.
And the sons of Elkanah ; Amasai , and Ahimoth.
\add As for\add* Elkanah : the sons of Elkanah ; Zophai his son , and Nahath his son ,\f + \fr 6.26 \ft Zophai: or, Zuph\f*
Eliab his son , Jeroham his son , Elkanah his son.
And the sons of Samuel ; the firstborn Vashni , and Abiah.\f + \fr 6.28 \ft Vashni: called also Joel\f*
The sons of Merari ; Mahli , Libni his son , Shimei his son , Uzza his son ,
Shimea his son , Haggiah his son , Asaiah his son. \p
And these \add are they\add* whom David set over the service of song in the house of the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*, after that the ark had rest.

And they ministered before the dwelling place of the tabernacle of the congregation with singing , until Solomon had built the house of the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* in Jerusalem : and \add then\add* they waited on their office according to their order.
And these \add are\add* they that waited with their children. Of the sons of the Kohathites : Heman a singer , the son of Joel , the son of Shemuel ,\f + \fr 6.33 \ft waited: Heb. stood\f*
The son of Elkanah , the son of Jeroham , the son of Eliel , the son of Toah ,
The son of Zuph , the son of Elkanah , the son of Mahath , the son of Amasai ,
The son of Elkanah , the son of Joel , the son of Azariah , the son of Zephaniah ,
The son of Tahath , the son of Assir , the son of Ebiasaph , the son of Korah ,
The son of Izhar , the son of Kohath , the son of Levi , the son of Israel.
And his brother Asaph , who stood on his right hand , \add even\add* Asaph the son of Berachiah , the son of Shimea ,
The son of Michael , the son of Baaseiah , the son of Malchiah ,
The son of Ethni , the son of Zerah , the son of Adaiah ,
The son of Ethan , the son of Zimmah , the son of Shimei ,
The son of Jahath , the son of Gershom , the son of Levi.
And their brethren the sons of Merari \add stood\add* on the left hand : Ethan the son of Kishi , the son of Abdi , the son of Malluch ,\f + \fr 6.44 \ft Kishi: or, Kushaiah\f*
The son of Hashabiah , the son of Amaziah , the son of Hilkiah ,
The son of Amzi , the son of Bani , the son of Shamer ,
The son of Mahli , the son of Mushi , the son of Merari , the son of Levi.
Their brethren also the Levites \add were\add* appointed unto all manner of service of the tabernacle of the house of God. \p

¶ But Aaron and his sons offered upon the altar of the burnt offering , and on the altar of incense , \add and were appointed\add* for all the work of the \add place\add* most holy , and to make an atonement for Israel , according to all that Moses the servant of God had commanded.
And these \add are\add* the sons of Aaron ; Eleazar his son , Phinehas his son , Abishua his son ,
Bukki his son , Uzzi his son , Zerahiah his son ,
Meraioth his son , Amariah his son , Ahitub his son ,
Zadok his son , Ahimaaz his son. \p
¶ Now these \add are\add* their dwelling places throughout their castles in their coasts , of the sons of Aaron , of the families of the Kohathites : for theirs was the lot.
And they gave them Hebron in the land of Judah , and the suburbs thereof round about it.
But the fields of the city , and the villages thereof, they gave to Caleb the son of Jephunneh.
And to the sons of Aaron they gave the cities of Judah, \add namely\add*, Hebron , \add the city\add* of refuge , and Libnah with her suburbs , and Jattir , and Eshtemoa , with their suburbs ,
And Hilen with her suburbs , Debir with her suburbs ,\f + \fr 6.58 \ft Hilen: or, Holon\f*
And Ashan with her suburbs , and Beth-shemesh with her suburbs :\f + \fr 6.59 \ft Ashan: or, Ain\f*

And out of the tribe of Benjamin ; Geba with her suburbs , and Alemeth with her suburbs , and Anathoth with her suburbs. All their cities throughout their families \add were\add* thirteen cities.\f + \fr 6.60 \ft Alemeth: or, Almon\f*

And unto the sons of Kohath , \add which were\add* left of the family of that tribe , \add were cities given\add* out of the half tribe , \add namely, out of\add* the half \add tribe\add* of Manasseh , by lot , ten cities.

And to the sons of Gershom throughout their families out of the tribe of Issachar , and out of the tribe of Asher , and out of the tribe of Naphtali , and out of the tribe of Manasseh in Bashan , thirteen cities.
Unto the sons of Merari \add were given\add* by lot , throughout their families , out of the tribe of Reuben , and out of the tribe of Gad , and out of the tribe of Zebulun , twelve cities.
And the children of Israel gave to the Levites \add these\add* cities with their suburbs.

And they gave by lot out of the tribe of the children of Judah , and out of the tribe of the children of Simeon , and out of the tribe of the children of Benjamin , these cities , which are called by \add their\add* names.
And \add the residue\add* of the families of the sons of Kohath had cities of their coasts out of the tribe of Ephraim.
And they gave unto them, \add of\add* the cities of refuge , Shechem in mount Ephraim with her suburbs ; \add they gave\add* also Gezer with her suburbs ,
And Jokmeam with her suburbs , and Beth-horon with her suburbs ,
And Aijalon with her suburbs , and Gath-rimmon with her suburbs :
And out of the half tribe of Manasseh ; Aner with her suburbs , and Bileam with her suburbs , for the family of the remnant of the sons of Kohath.
Unto the sons of Gershom \add were given\add* out of the family of the half tribe of Manasseh , Golan in Bashan with her suburbs , and Ashtaroth with her suburbs :
And out of the tribe of Issachar ; Kedesh with her suburbs , Daberath with her suburbs ,
And Ramoth with her suburbs , and Anem with her suburbs :
And out of the tribe of Asher ; Mashal with her suburbs , and Abdon with her suburbs ,
And Hukok with her suburbs , and Rehob with her suburbs :
And out of the tribe of Naphtali ; Kedesh in Galilee with her suburbs , and Hammon with her suburbs , and Kirjathaim with her suburbs.
Unto the rest of the children of Merari \add were given\add* out of the tribe of Zebulun , Rimmon with her suburbs , Tabor with her suburbs :
And on the other side Jordan by Jericho , on the east side of Jordan , \add were given them\add* out of the tribe of Reuben , Bezer in the wilderness with her suburbs , and Jahzah with her suburbs ,
Kedemoth also with her suburbs , and Mephaath with her suburbs :
And out of the tribe of Gad ; Ramoth in Gilead with her suburbs , and Mahanaim with her suburbs ,
And Heshbon with her suburbs , and Jazer with her suburbs.
